    "text": "there are a plethora of base op- tions that can really make a non- alcoholic drink look and taste nearly identical to an alcoholic one,\" says Joel Atlas, a mixologist at the Avery Bar at the Ritz-Carl- ton, Boston. \"The bloom of op- tions has really picked up in the last year and a half to two years.\"",
