    "text": "\"[Mocktails] are certainly marketed more in January, but the truth of it all is that the non- alcoholic or low-ABV consumer is sustaining through much of the year,\" says Nick Moniz, gen- eral manager of Banners Kitch- en and Tap and Hub Hall.",
