    "text": "This industry hangout takes dive-bar food to another level — they pioneered dressed-up tater tots and mac-and-cheese before it was fashionable. Here, $5 cans of Miller High Life share real es- tate with cheeky mocktails like the Phony Negroni, a nonalco- holic version of the classic, and Island Life, Baby, made with a booze-free, floral Fluère Botanic Blend. Good for: dive-bar-dining without the buzz. 3 Beacon St., Somerville, 617-576-0006",
